# FunkFit environment variables.
# Copy to ".env" (gitignored) and fill in your FatSecret credentials.
#
# Get free credentials at https://platform.fatsecret.com/ (Platform API).
# These enable live food search on the "Log food" screen. Without them, the
# app still works — you just log foods manually.
#
# NOTE: EXPO_PUBLIC_* values are embedded in the app bundle, so the client
# secret is only semi-private. For a production release, proxy these calls
# through a small backend instead of shipping the secret in the app.

EXPO_PUBLIC_FATSECRET_CLIENT_ID=
EXPO_PUBLIC_FATSECRET_CLIENT_SECRET=
